#: erpnext/selling/doctype/selling_settings/selling_settings.json
msgid "Enabling this will do the following:\n"
"<ul style=\"padding-left:16px\">\n"
"<li>Make the rate column of all Packed/Bundle Items tables editable.</li>\n"
"<li>Calculate the prices of all <a href=\"/desk/product-bundle\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Product Bundles</a> in the Items table, based on the prices of its child Items, specified in the Packed/Bundle Items table. </li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"Note: If this is enabled, updating the rate of the Product Bundle in the Items table will not change its price. It will get reset to the price based on its Child Items on saving the doc."
msgstr "Buni yoqish quyidagilarni bajaradi:\n"
"<ul style=\"padding-left:16px\">\n"
"<li>Barcha Qadoqlangan/Paketli Mahsulotlar jadvallarining narx ustunini tahrirlanadigan qilib qo'ying.</li>\n"
"<li>Mahsulotlar jadvalidagi barcha <a href=\"/desk/product-bundle\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mahsulotlar to'plamlari</a> narxlarini, Qadoqlangan/Paketli Mahsulotlar jadvalida ko'rsatilgan kichik buyumlar narxlariga asoslanib hisoblang. </li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"Eslatma: Agar bu yoqilgan bo'lsa, \"Mahsulotlar\" jadvalidagi \"Mahsulotlar to'plami\" narxini yangilash uning narxini o'zgartirmaydi. Hujjat saqlangandan so'ng, u o'zining kichik buyumlari asosida narxga qayta o'rnatiladi."

